Yes, please.

11
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:36,880
Do you want any milk?

12
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,650
No, thank you.

13
00:00:38,650 --> 00:00:41,720
I don't like milk in my coffee.

14
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:45,420
I like black coffee.

15
